{"tid":1176304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社：部分香港法官對修訂《逃犯條例》深感不安","createTime":"2019-05-29T06:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:14:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1c5263ce994f80441dae9d49f7a5030d7812e8","tid":1176304,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"路透社報道，部分香港法官對政府推動修訂《逃犯條例》深感不安，認為是不可行。<br />\n<br />\n路透社在香港訪問3名不願透露姓名的資深法官及12名律師，他們表示，今次修例是香港司法制度面臨的最嚴峻挑戰，會愈來愈困擾香港的商界、政界和外交界。他們又說，根據香港的普通法制度，引渡是基於接收國有公平審訊和人道懲處的推定，但他們認為，內地的法律體制未能做到。<br />\n<br />\n受訪的法官又說，擔心假如試圖不將備受矚目的疑犯引渡返內地，會受到來自北京的批評和政治壓力。但如果同意引渡要求，亦會受到社會部分人的指責。"},{"pid":"747a45711661508223f0bb0e46e0ffb7e365e277","tid":1176304,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459907-20190529.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459907-20190529.htm&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=f7763fde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1459907-20190529.htm&h=7758e780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1459907-20190529.htm</a>"},{"pid":"09cf9ec081bedca11554ce0bdcd8e3c401f9c5a7","tid":1176304,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-politics-extradition-judges/exclusive-hong-kong-judges-see-risks-in-proposed-extradition-changes-idUSKCN1SZ09U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-politics-extradition-judges%2Fexclusive-hong-kong-judges-see-risks-in-proposed-extradition-changes-idUSKCN1SZ09U&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=2e07b14c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hon